 <Dev2customScriptTB>lt;scriptgt;$(document).ready(function(){ 		$("#Dev2DatabaseServiceSetupFilter").keyup(function(){ 					$('#Dev2DatabaseServiceSetupInputTestData tr').not(':first').not(':last').remove();			try{ 				var services = $.parseJSON('[[Dev2DatabaseServiceSetupInformationSchema]]'); 			var procedures = new Array();			for(var i = 0; i lt; services.Procedures.length;i++){				var proc = services.Procedures[i];				procedures[i] = proc.ProcedureName;			}							var functions = new Array();			for(var i = 0; i lt; services.Functions.length;i++){				var _function = services.Functions[i];				functions[i] = _function.FunctionName;			}								$("#Dev2DatabaseServiceSetupActivityList").html(''); 				var opt = ""; 				opt += 'lt;option style="font-weight:bold"gt;Stored Procedureslt;/optiongt;';				for(var i=0;ilt;procedures.length;i++){ 					var value = $("#Dev2DatabaseServiceSetupFilter").val().toUpperCase(); 					var tmp = procedures[i]; 					var tmpSearch = procedures[i].toUpperCase(); 					if(tmpSearch.indexOf(value) gt;= 0){ 						opt += "lt;optiongt;"+tmp+"lt;/optiongt;"; 					} 				} 				opt += 'lt;option style="font-weight:bold"gt;Functionslt;/optiongt;';				for(var i=0;ilt;functions.length;i++){ 					var value = $("#Dev2DatabaseServiceSetupFilter").val().toUpperCase(); 					var tmp = functions[i]; 					var tmpSearch = functions[i].toUpperCase(); 					if(tmpSearch.indexOf(value) gt;= 0){ 						opt += "lt;optiongt;"+tmp+"lt;/optiongt;"; 					} 				} 				$("#Dev2DatabaseServiceSetupActivityList").html(opt); 			}catch(e){ 			} 		});	});lt;/scriptgt; </Dev2customScriptTB>
